1
00:00:07,166 --> 00:00:09,932
[ CHILD #1 CRYING ]
IT HURTS!

2
00:00:09,966 --> 00:00:13,266
[ WOMAN SHRIEKS ]

3
00:00:14,032 --> 00:00:15,899
MOMMY!

4
00:00:15,932 --> 00:00:17,899
[ PANTING ]

5
00:00:17,932 --> 00:00:20,266
[ CRYING CONTINUES ]

6
00:00:20,299 --> 00:00:22,766
OH, RIN, WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

7
00:00:22,799 --> 00:00:25,266
[ WOMAN ]
GET THE PRINCIPAL.
GET THE PRINCIPAL!

8
00:00:28,132 --> 00:00:30,699
[ GASPING ]

9
00:00:31,866 --> 00:00:34,232
[ SCREAMING ]

10
00:00:51,366 --> 00:00:53,666
♪ [ CHORUS SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

11
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,650
[ RIN ]
VATICAN?

12
00:02:09,683 --> 00:02:11,883
SENIOR EXORCIST
FIRST CLASS?

13
00:02:11,916 --> 00:02:14,316
HERE'S MY LICENSE AND BADGE
IF YOU WANT PROOF.

14
00:02:14,350 --> 00:02:16,383
OF COURSE.
YES. THANK YOU.

15
00:02:16,416 --> 00:02:19,616
AND I'M INTERMEDIATE EXORCIST
KAORU TSUBAKI.

16
00:02:19,650 --> 00:02:23,483
NO, IT'S COOL.
NO NEED FOR SHOW AND TELL.
I TRUST YOU.

17
00:02:23,516 --> 00:02:27,083
ANYWAY, I GOTTA GO TAKE HIM
TO JAPAN BRANCH H.Q.

18
00:02:27,116 --> 00:02:32,016
I ALSO WANNA TALK TO MEPHISTO.
IF HE'S GOT A PROBLEM WITH THAT,
DRAG HIM TO ME IF YOU HAVE TO.

19
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:34,583
- YES.
- COME ON, GET UP.

20
00:02:34,616 --> 00:02:36,383
[ GRUNTS ]
I GOT A MILLION QUESTIONS,

21
00:02:36,416 --> 00:02:38,050
AND I'D BETTER LIKE
YOUR ANSWERS.

22
00:02:38,083 --> 00:02:39,483
[ MUFFLED PROTESTS ]

23
00:02:39,516 --> 00:02:42,416
EXCUSE ME.
RIN'S INJURED
AND NEEDS TREATMENT.

24
00:02:42,450 --> 00:02:44,783
- CAN'T THIS WAIT A BIT?
- [ RIN GRUNTING ]

25
00:02:44,816 --> 00:02:46,850
OH, DON'T YOU WORRY.
HE'LL BE FINE.

26
00:02:46,883 --> 00:02:49,216
BUT, BABY, YOU SMELL LIKE MILK,
SO CHILL OUT.

27
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:50,916
I SMELL LIKE MILK?

28
00:02:53,716 --> 00:02:55,950
HOW LONG ARE WE
GONNA WAIT?
I HAVE NO IDEA.

29
00:02:55,983 --> 00:02:59,250
[ KAMIKI ] UH, SIR?
[ SUGURO ] WHAT THE HECK'S
GOING ON AROUND HERE?

30
00:02:59,283 --> 00:03:01,716
LISTEN UP, CLASS.
TODAY'S MISSION IS OVER.

31
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:03,950
YOU CAN ALL RETURN
TO YOUR DORMS FOR NOW.

32
00:03:03,983 --> 00:03:06,783
[ RIN ]
LET ME GO!
I CAN'T BREATHE, DAMN IT!

33
00:03:06,816 --> 00:03:08,783
- [ GASPS ]
- [ SHIMA ]
WELL, THAT SUCKS.

34
00:03:08,816 --> 00:03:11,216
NOW I'M JEALOUS.
[ MIWA ]
SHIMA!

35
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:13,883
[ SHIMA ]
HOLD ON A SEC.
WHO IS THAT HOTTIE?

36
00:03:13,916 --> 00:03:16,283
[ MIWA ]
SHE'S WEARING PANTS
FROM A BOY'S UNIFORM.

37
00:03:16,316 --> 00:03:17,716
COULD THAT BE YAMADA?

38
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:20,183
NO WAY!
[ SUGURO ]
TYPICAL OKUMURA.

39
00:03:20,216 --> 00:03:22,283
GUY'S ALWAYS GETTING
INTO A JAM.

40
00:03:22,316 --> 00:03:25,150
[ KAMIKI ]
HEY, HOLD IT RIGHT THERE.

41
00:03:25,183 --> 00:03:27,483
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT'S GOING ON?

42
00:03:27,516 --> 00:03:30,883
I'M NOT SURE YET.
ALL I KNOW IS
IT'S NOT HIS FAULT.

43
00:03:30,916 --> 00:03:32,383
[ KAMIKI ]
HUH?

44
00:03:33,316 --> 00:03:35,050
IS IT?

45
00:03:35,083 --> 00:03:36,850
[ RIN ]
WHERE ARE YOU TAKING ME?

46
00:03:36,883 --> 00:03:40,950
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU NEVER HAD A REASON
TO COME TO THE BASE BEFORE NOW.

47
00:03:40,983 --> 00:03:42,616
THE BASE?

48
00:03:44,683 --> 00:03:47,416
[ CREAKING ]

49
00:03:52,816 --> 00:03:54,516
[ DOOR CREAKING ]

50
00:03:59,816 --> 00:04:01,150
IS THIS IT?

51
00:04:01,183 --> 00:04:04,183
YEP. THIS IS THE JAPAN BRANCH
OF THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

52
00:04:04,216 --> 00:04:05,650
[ GRUNTS ]

53
00:04:08,250 --> 00:04:10,450
THE MAIN HEADQUARTERS
ARE IN THE VATICAN,

54
00:04:10,483 --> 00:04:13,150
RIGHT UNDERNEATH
SAINT PIERRE PAULO'S BASILICA.

55
00:04:13,183 --> 00:04:16,650
ALL THE BRANCHES
FROM ALL OVER THE GLOBE
ARE RUN FROM THAT LOCATION.

56
00:04:16,683 --> 00:04:19,283
THE ORDER'S BEEN AROUND
FOR MORE THAN 2,000 YEARS...

57
00:04:19,316 --> 00:04:21,116
PROTECTING THE WORLD
FROM MONSTERS.

58
00:04:21,150 --> 00:04:22,550
OH.

59
00:04:22,583 --> 00:04:24,716
[ MEPHISTO ]
QUITE TRUE.

60
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:28,616
WELCOME TO THE JAPAN BRANCH OF
THE KNIGHTS OF THE TRUE CROSS.

61
00:04:28,650 --> 00:04:31,150
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
IN AGES, SHURA.

62
00:04:31,183 --> 00:04:35,816
AND WHAT A SURPRISE IT IS
TO FIND THAT YOU'D INFILTRATED
OUR CRAM SCHOOL TO SPY ON US.

63
00:04:35,850 --> 00:04:38,950
YOUR DISGUISE WAS INSPIRED.
I HAD NO CLUE.

64
00:04:38,983 --> 00:04:42,316
MEPHISTO, HOW ABOUT
WE CUT TO THE CHASE?

65
00:04:42,350 --> 00:04:45,550
WHY'D YOU HIDE THE EXISTENCE
OF THE SON OF SATAN
FROM THE ORDER?

66
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:47,850
I DIDN'T HIDE ANYTHING
FROM ANYONE.

67
00:04:47,883 --> 00:04:51,483
YES, I TOOK HIM IN,
BUT IT WAS ALL FOR THE SAKE
OF THE ORDER AND ITS FUTURE.

68
00:04:51,516 --> 00:04:53,350
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

69
00:04:53,383 --> 00:04:57,083
WE TRAIN THE SON OF SATAN
AND USE HIM
AS A WEAPON FOR THE ORDER.

70
00:04:57,116 --> 00:05:01,250
LOOK, FOR THE LAST 2,000 YEARS,
WE EXORCISTS
HAVE BEEN ON THE DEFENSIVE.

71
00:05:01,283 --> 00:05:04,416
BUT WITH HIM,
NOW WE HAVE THE CHANCE
TO TAKE THE INITIATIVE.

72
00:05:05,650 --> 00:05:07,683
YOU DIDN'T ANSWER MY QUESTION,

73
00:05:07,716 --> 00:05:09,783
SO I'M GONNA ASK YOU
ONE MORE TIME--

74
00:05:09,816 --> 00:05:11,916
WHY DIDN'T YOU REPORT THIS
TO THE VATICAN?

75
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:15,083
WELL, LOOK AT HIM.
HIS POWER ISN'T AT
ITS FULL POTENTIAL.

76
00:05:15,116 --> 00:05:21,216
YOU KNOW THE GRIGORI
WOULD NEVER BE CONVINCED
BY A HALF-FINISHED PROJECT.

77
00:05:21,250 --> 00:05:23,050
ONE MORE QUESTION.

78
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:26,416
WAS SHIRO FUJIMOTO ALSO INVOLVED
IN THIS SCHEME OF YOURS?

79
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:28,116
I SWEAR, THERE'S NO SCHEME.

80
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:31,416
FUJIMOTO RAISED HIM
UNTIL THE BOY BECAME AWARE
OF HIS POWER.

81
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:34,116
ALL I'M DOING
IS ACTING AS HIS GUARDIAN.

82
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:35,683
I SEE.

83
00:05:35,716 --> 00:05:38,416
EITHER WAY, I'M STILL
GONNA REPORT THIS.

84
00:05:38,450 --> 00:05:40,850
BEFORE I DO,
I WANNA INTERROGATE THE KID.

85
00:05:40,883 --> 00:05:43,083
HOPE YOU DON'T MIND
IF I USE THE GREAT CELL.

86
00:05:43,116 --> 00:05:44,983
PLEASE.
MAKE YOURSELF AT HOME.

87
00:05:45,016 --> 00:05:48,150
I'M SURE YOU'LL FIND HIM
TO BE QUITE THE AMUSING SUBJECT.

88
00:05:48,183 --> 00:05:50,616
HUH. YOU'RE COOL
AS A CUCUMBER.

89
00:05:50,650 --> 00:05:52,616
WE'LL SEE WHAT YOU'RE LIKE
AFTER I'M DONE.

90
00:05:52,650 --> 00:05:54,583
WAIT, SHURA, JUST A MOMENT.

91
00:05:54,616 --> 00:05:56,516
YOU DON'T HAVE TO INTERROGATE
MY BROTHER.

92
00:05:56,550 --> 00:05:58,883
I CAN TELL YOU ANYTHING
YOU WANT TO KNOW.

93
00:05:58,916 --> 00:06:02,116
YEAH, YOU'RE A LITTLE TALLER
THAN THE LAST TIME I SAW YOU.

94
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:05,683
BUT IN A LOT OF WAYS,
YOU'RE STILL THE KID
I USED TO KNOW.

95
00:06:05,716 --> 00:06:08,116
GO HOME
AND GET SOME SLEEP.
I'M OUT.

96
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,750
SHURA--

97
00:06:12,022 --> 00:06:14,189
[ DOORS OPENING ]

98
00:06:17,255 --> 00:06:18,889
[ RIN GRUNTING ]

99
00:06:22,555 --> 00:06:24,122
WANNA TELL ME
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND?

100
00:06:24,155 --> 00:06:26,055
YOU'VE BEEN AWFULLY QUIET
THIS WHOLE TIME.

101
00:06:26,089 --> 00:06:29,022
BACK THERE YOU SAID
YOU KNEW MY OLD MAN AND YUKIO.

102
00:06:29,055 --> 00:06:32,955
UH-HUH. I WAS SORT OF
A DISCIPLE OF SHIRO FUJIMOTO'S.

103
00:06:32,989 --> 00:06:34,255
REALLY?

104
00:06:36,155 --> 00:06:38,289
YOU MEAN YOU WERE LIKE
A NUN OR SOMETHING?

105
00:06:38,322 --> 00:06:41,789
YEAH, RIGHT.
I NEVER PRAYED TO GOD
EVEN ONCE IN MY LIFE.

106
00:06:41,822 --> 00:06:45,055
GROWING UP, I LIVED
IN SOME AWFUL PLACES.

107
00:06:46,922 --> 00:06:50,055
EVERY DAY WAS A STRUGGLE
JUST TO STAY ALIVE.

108
00:06:50,089 --> 00:06:53,655
AND THEN OUT OF NOWHERE
THIS MAN CAME AND SAVED ME,

109
00:06:53,689 --> 00:06:56,322
AND HE WAS SHIRO FUJIMOTO.

110
00:07:01,622 --> 00:07:03,022
[ SCREECHES ]

111
00:07:06,289 --> 00:07:07,855
[ COCKS ]

112
00:07:12,322 --> 00:07:17,155
BUT THAT WAS A LONG TIME
BEFORE YOU AND YOUR BROTHER
WERE BORN.

113
00:07:17,189 --> 00:07:19,789
[ GASPING ]

114
00:07:19,822 --> 00:07:23,922
WHAT'S WRONG?
DID YOU HURT YOURSELF
AT THE AMUSEMENT PARK?

115
00:07:25,522 --> 00:07:27,655
- [ GASPS ]
- DUMBASS.

116
00:07:27,689 --> 00:07:30,522
YOU JUST FELL FOR THE OLDEST
TRICK IN THE BOOK.

117
00:07:30,555 --> 00:07:32,722
HOW MANY TIMES YOU GONNA GIVE
THIS THING AWAY?

118
00:07:32,755 --> 00:07:35,355
YOU GOT A PROBLEM
HANGING ONTO IT, KID?

119
00:07:35,389 --> 00:07:38,889
OF COURSE I DON'T.
GIVE IT BACK!

120
00:07:38,922 --> 00:07:40,655
[ SHOUTING ]

121
00:07:42,722 --> 00:07:44,855
[ THINKING ]
THE SWORD HASN'T BEEN DRAWN.

122
00:07:44,889 --> 00:07:48,355
BUT HIS POWER--
KURIKARA CAN'T CONTROL IT
ANYMORE.

123
00:07:50,555 --> 00:07:53,822
[ SHURA ]
WHAT? YOU WANT ME TO MENTOR
THAT FOUR-EYED CHICKEN?

124
00:07:53,855 --> 00:07:57,622
[ FUJIMOTO ]
NO. I'D LIKE YOU TO MENTOR
THE OTHER ONE.

125
00:07:57,655 --> 00:07:59,922
YOU'LL LIKE HIM.
HE'S AMUSING.

126
00:07:59,955 --> 00:08:02,055
WHY ARE YOU ASKING ME
TO DO IT?

127
00:08:02,089 --> 00:08:06,022
BECAUSE YOU'RE AN EXPERT
AT HANDLING DEMON SWORDS.

128
00:08:06,055 --> 00:08:08,589
ARE YOU GONNA GIVE HIM
A DEMON SWORD?

129
00:08:11,189 --> 00:08:14,622
PUTTING SOMETHING THAT DANGEROUS
IN THE HANDS OF A LITTLE KID'S
INSANE.

130
00:08:14,655 --> 00:08:16,889
HELL, YOU AND I BOTH KNOW THAT!

131
00:08:16,922 --> 00:08:20,222
YES, I DO, BUT I DON'T
HAVE A CHOICE.

132
00:08:20,255 --> 00:08:23,422
IF SOMETHING
SHOULD HAPPEN TO ME,
HE'S GOING TO NEED HELP.

133
00:08:23,455 --> 00:08:27,322
SO, PLEASE, TEACH HIM
THE PROPER WAY
TO USE THE SWORD.

134
00:08:27,355 --> 00:08:29,055
I'M BEGGING YOU.

135
00:08:31,122 --> 00:08:33,189
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU?

136
00:08:33,222 --> 00:08:37,722
YOU WERE ALWAYS COOL,
CALM AND POWERFUL--
THE BEST EXORCIST IN THE ORDER.

137
00:08:37,755 --> 00:08:40,489
BUT NOW THAT YOU'RE OLD,
YOU'RE GETTING SCARED TOO?

138
00:08:40,522 --> 00:08:42,789
YOU TOSS ME OUT
LIKE I'M YESTERDAY'S GARBAGE,

139
00:08:42,822 --> 00:08:46,155
AND NOW YOU COME HERE
TRYING TO DUMP THAT KID ONTO ME?

140
00:08:48,422 --> 00:08:51,122
JUST GET OUT OF HERE.
DON'T COME BACK.

141
00:08:57,689 --> 00:09:01,255
SHIRO, YOU WERE
THE GREATEST TEACHER.

142
00:09:01,289 --> 00:09:04,055
I REALLY WANTED
TO BELIEVE THAT.

143
00:09:06,255 --> 00:09:08,322
DEVOUR THE EIGHT PRINCESSES.

144
00:09:09,455 --> 00:09:11,722
SLAY THE SERPENT.

145
00:09:17,789 --> 00:09:19,889
WHAT THE--
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

146
00:09:19,922 --> 00:09:21,822
YOU SAID YOU WERE
THE OLD MAN'S DISCIPLE.

147
00:09:21,855 --> 00:09:23,822
BUT THIS COMES
RIGHT FROM THE TOP.

148
00:09:23,855 --> 00:09:26,589
AND I'M A SENIOR INSPECTOR,
SO ON THE DAY SHIRO DIED,

149
00:09:26,622 --> 00:09:29,255
THE VATICAN SENT ME
ON A SECRET MISSION.

150
00:09:29,289 --> 00:09:33,255
THEY SUSPECTED SHIRO FUJIMOTO
AND MEPHISTO PHELES
HAD BEEN CONSPIRING...

151
00:09:33,289 --> 00:09:35,255
EVER SINCE THE BLUE NIGHT.

152
00:09:35,289 --> 00:09:38,855
THE VATICAN THOUGHT
THE TWO OF THEM MIGHT BE HIDING
SOMETHING CONNECTED TO SATAN,

153
00:09:38,889 --> 00:09:41,622
SO THEY SENT ME IN
TO INVESTIGATE.

154
00:09:42,855 --> 00:09:45,155
BUT HERE'S THE FUN PART.

155
00:09:45,189 --> 00:09:49,422
IF I FOUND OUT THERE WAS
A CONSPIRACY THAT WAS TIED
INTO ANYTHING SATANIC,

156
00:09:49,455 --> 00:09:53,789
I WAS GIVEN PERMISSION
TO EXTERMINATE IT
ON THE SPOT.

157
00:09:53,822 --> 00:09:56,222
- EXTERMINATE?
- THAT'S WHAT I SAID.

158
00:09:56,255 --> 00:09:59,222
YOU KNOW THOSE BLUE FLAMES
SPROUTING OUT OF YOUR BODY?

159
00:09:59,255 --> 00:10:03,522
EVEN TO THE UNTRAINED EYE,
THAT'S PROOF POSITIVE
YOU'RE THE SON OF SATAN.

160
00:10:03,555 --> 00:10:06,189
SO AS ORDERED,
I'M GOING TO KILL YOU.

161
00:10:06,222 --> 00:10:10,222
GUESS THE DISCIPLE'S
GOTTA CLEAN UP
HER MENTOR'S MESS AFTER ALL.

162
00:10:10,255 --> 00:10:12,422
YOU'RE GONNA--
HEY, WAIT.

163
00:10:12,455 --> 00:10:15,289
KIRIGAKURE SWORD TECHNIQUE,
SNAKE FANG!

164
00:10:16,655 --> 00:10:18,755
- [ GASPS ]
- [ CRASHING ]

165
00:10:18,789 --> 00:10:20,722
SOUNDS LIKE THEY'RE HAVING FUN.

166
00:10:20,755 --> 00:10:23,222
NO USE TRYING
TO INTERVENE THOUGH.

167
00:10:23,255 --> 00:10:27,255
THE GREAT CELL CAN ONLY BE
UNLOCKED BY A SENIOR EXORCIST.

168
00:10:27,289 --> 00:10:31,622
THERE'S NOTHING WE CAN DO NOW
BUT SIT BACK, RELAX AND WAIT
FOR THE INTERROGATION TO END.

169
00:10:34,022 --> 00:10:35,655
[ RIN COUGHING ]

170
00:10:37,022 --> 00:10:41,189
WHAT THE HELL?
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

171
00:10:41,222 --> 00:10:42,655
[ SHOUTS ]

172
00:10:50,255 --> 00:10:54,622
THAT DEMON WAS STRONG,
BUT SHE'S--
SHE'S WAY STRONG!

173
00:10:56,755 --> 00:11:00,089
[ SHURA ]
SHIRO, WHAT WERE YOU
TRYING TO DO?

174
00:11:00,122 --> 00:11:01,655
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING?

175
00:11:01,689 --> 00:11:05,655
YOU IGNORED THE VATICAN
AND RAISED THE SON OF SATAN.

176
00:11:05,689 --> 00:11:07,455
[ MEPHISTO ]
WE TRAIN THE SON OF SATAN...

177
00:11:07,489 --> 00:11:09,489
AND USE HIM AS A WEAPON
FOR THE ORDER.

178
00:11:09,522 --> 00:11:11,789
[ SHURA ]
WAS THIS YOUR DYING WISH?

179
00:11:11,822 --> 00:11:15,122
IS THIS WHAT YOU RISKED
YOUR LIFE FOR?
WHAT YOU DIED FOR?

180
00:11:16,722 --> 00:11:19,555
DAMN IT, SHIRO!

181
00:11:19,589 --> 00:11:21,622
[ GRUNTING ]

182
00:11:26,122 --> 00:11:27,955
MAN, TALK ABOUT DELUDED.

183
00:11:27,989 --> 00:11:30,522
EVEN IF I DID TRAIN
THIS GOOD-FOR-NOTHING PUNK,

184
00:11:30,555 --> 00:11:32,555
HE'D NEVER BE ABLE TO PUT
A SCRATCH ON SATAN.

185
00:11:32,589 --> 00:11:34,289
SAY WHAT?

186
00:11:35,655 --> 00:11:37,055
YOU WERE A COWARD, SHIRO.

187
00:11:37,089 --> 00:11:38,955
INSTEAD OF FIGHTING
LIKE A MAN,

188
00:11:38,989 --> 00:11:41,489
YOU DECIDED TO HANG ON
TO YOUR IMPOSSIBLE HOPES.

189
00:11:41,522 --> 00:11:44,789
NO! YOU'RE WRONG.
MY DAD WASN'T A COWARD.

190
00:11:44,822 --> 00:11:47,855
HE DIED PROTECTING ME.

191
00:11:47,889 --> 00:11:51,722
- I SAY HE WAS A COWARD.
- YOU DON'T KNOW A DAMN THING.

192
00:11:51,755 --> 00:11:54,022
SO SHUT THE HELL UP!

193
00:11:57,489 --> 00:11:59,355
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

194
00:12:05,522 --> 00:12:07,755
I DON'T CARE
IF YOU WERE HIS DISCIPLE.

195
00:12:07,789 --> 00:12:10,255
I'M NOT GONNA TAKE
YOUR CRAP ANYMORE.

196
00:12:10,289 --> 00:12:12,689
AND DON'T DIS MY OLD MAN!

197
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:25,240
[ GRUNTING, BLOWS LANDING ]

198
00:12:38,473 --> 00:12:40,073
[ SIGHS ]

199
00:12:40,106 --> 00:12:41,906
THIS KID'S OUTTA CONTROL.

200
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:44,040
HIS ATTACKS
ARE ALL OVER THE PLACE.

201
00:12:44,073 --> 00:12:47,440
HE'S GOT NO FIGHTING TECHNIQUE.
IT'S PATHETIC.

202
00:12:47,473 --> 00:12:50,206
WHAT HAPPENED?
YOU WEREN'T GONNA TAKE
MY CRAP ANYMORE.

203
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,773
IF YOU DON'T ATTACK, I WILL.

204
00:12:52,806 --> 00:12:55,606
KIRIGAKURE SWORD TECHNIQUE,
RATTLE!

205
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:57,606
[ HISSING ]

206
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,506
[ SHOUTING ]

207
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:03,673
- [ GASPS ]
- [ SHOUTING ]

208
00:13:03,706 --> 00:13:05,806
[ SCREAMING ]

209
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,806
[ GRUNTS, SCREAMS ]

210
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:10,373
GEEZ, YOU'RE A MAN.
DIE WITH SOME DIGNITY.

211
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:16,873
THERE'S NO WAY I'M GONNA LET
MYSELF GET KILLED
IN A PLACE LIKE THIS.

212
00:13:16,906 --> 00:13:18,673
YOU HEAR?

213
00:13:18,706 --> 00:13:23,506
I SWORE ON HIS GRAVE
THAT SOMEDAY I WAS GONNA BE
A GREAT EXORCIST LIKE HIM,

214
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,773
AND THAT I'D BEAT THE SHIT
OUT OF SATAN!

215
00:13:25,806 --> 00:13:27,640
YOU'RE GONNA BEAT THE SHIT
OUT OF SATAN?

216
00:13:27,673 --> 00:13:32,440
YEAH. I'M GONNA BE A PALADIN,
THE MOST POWERFUL EXORCIST
OF ALL.

217
00:13:32,473 --> 00:13:37,540
AND THEN ONCE I'M A PALADIN,
EVERYONE'S GONNA KNOW
THAT MY DAD WAS RIGHT ALL ALONG.

218
00:13:37,573 --> 00:13:40,906
OH, A PALADIN, HUH?
DON'T MAKE ME LAUGH,
YOU BRAT.

219
00:13:40,940 --> 00:13:43,140
[ FUJIMOTO ]
YOU'LL LIKE HIM.
HE'S AMUSING.

220
00:13:46,506 --> 00:13:48,940
[ CHUCKLING ]

221
00:13:52,773 --> 00:13:55,506
[ LAUGHS ]

222
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:01,406
YOU WERE RIGHT.
HE'S FUNNY.

223
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:05,340
OH, MAN. OR MAYBE I'M
THE RIDICULOUS ONE.
I DON'T KNOW.

224
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,473
[ DOORS OPENING ]

225
00:14:12,873 --> 00:14:14,940
YOU REALLY LOVED SHIRO,
DIDN'T YOU?

226
00:14:14,973 --> 00:14:17,673
HUH? I--
I DIDN'T SAY THAT.

227
00:14:17,706 --> 00:14:21,706
[ SHURA ]
YOU WEREN'T RAISING A WEAPON
ALL THESE YEARS, SHIRO.

228
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:24,640
NAH. YOU WERE RAISING...

229
00:14:24,673 --> 00:14:27,773
A SON.

230
00:14:27,806 --> 00:14:31,440
[ RIN ]
OW! THAT STINGS!
TAKE IT EASY.

231
00:14:31,473 --> 00:14:33,140
WHAT HAPPENED IN THERE?

232
00:14:33,173 --> 00:14:35,040
NOTHING. THE USUAL.
I DON'T KNOW.

233
00:14:35,073 --> 00:14:36,140
[ DOOR OPENS ]

234
00:14:36,173 --> 00:14:38,106
[ SHURA ]
HERE, CATCH.

235
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:40,106
WHAT'S THE DEAL
WITH THIS THING?

236
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:42,473
WHAT ARE YOU, BLIND?
IT'S A WOODEN SWORD.

237
00:14:42,506 --> 00:14:45,273
- WHERE'S MY SWORD?
- I'M HOLDING ONTO IT
FOR NOW.

238
00:14:45,306 --> 00:14:47,273
TRUST ME, IT'S BETTER THIS WAY.

239
00:14:47,306 --> 00:14:50,473
WHO KNOWS WHEN AMAIMON'S
GONNA COME AROUND
AND SNATCH IT FROM YOU AGAIN?

240
00:14:50,506 --> 00:14:51,406
[ GASPS ]

241
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,940
IF YOU WANT IT BACK,
GET STRONGER.

242
00:14:53,973 --> 00:14:56,106
WHEN YOU CAN BEAT ME,
THEN YOU CAN HAVE IT.

243
00:14:56,140 --> 00:14:58,306
HERE'S YOUR CHANCE
TO PROVE IT, KID--

244
00:14:58,340 --> 00:15:00,906
THAT SHIRO WAS RIGHT
ABOUT YOU ALL ALONG.

245
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,506
[ GASPS ]

246
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:10,640
[ SHURA ]
I WON'T SEND A REPORT
TO THE VATICAN YET.

247
00:15:10,673 --> 00:15:14,440
I'M GONNA KEEP AN EYE
ON RIN OKUMURA
FOR A WHILE THOUGH.

248
00:15:14,473 --> 00:15:18,406
I'D LIKE YOU TO FIND A PLACE
FOR ME HERE AT THE JAPAN BRANCH.

249
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:22,840
AS YOU WISH. ACTUALLY,
THAT'S A WONDERFUL IDEA.

250
00:15:22,873 --> 00:15:27,706
IT WOULD BE REASSURING
TO HAVE SUCH A CAPABLE EXORCIST
IN OUR MIDST.

251
00:15:27,740 --> 00:15:29,940
HUH.
WE'RE DONE HERE.

252
00:15:29,973 --> 00:15:32,173
NO. YOU CAN'T LEAVE JUST YET.

253
00:15:32,206 --> 00:15:36,673
I HAVE THIS FABULOUS GREEN TEA
ICE CREAM I ORDERED FROM KYOTO.
HAVE SOME WITH ME.

254
00:15:36,706 --> 00:15:40,640
MEPHISTO, YOU WANNA CUT THE CRAP
AND JUST TELL ME
WHAT YOU'RE UP TO?

255
00:15:40,673 --> 00:15:44,940
WHY, NOTHING.
I ONLY DESIRE PEACE
FOR HUMANITY AND ASSIAH.

256
00:15:44,973 --> 00:15:46,806
THIS IS MY HOME NOW.

257
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:49,406
I ABANDONED GEHENNA
TO LIVE HERE, REMEMBER?

258
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:51,640
LOOK, DON'T FORGET
YOU'RE STILL A DEMON.

259
00:15:51,673 --> 00:15:55,506
OUR SUPERIORS DON'T TRUST YOU
AT ALL, AND I, FOR ONE,
DON'T BLAME THEM.

260
00:15:55,540 --> 00:15:58,873
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

261
00:15:58,906 --> 00:16:00,673
[ AMAIMON ]
MY POOR BROTHER.

262
00:16:00,706 --> 00:16:02,906
NO ONE TRUSTS YOU
AT ALL, DO THEY?

263
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:08,573
AMAIMON, YOU AND I
HAVE MUCH TO SPEAK ABOUT
REGARDING YOUR RECENT ANTICS.

264
00:16:20,206 --> 00:16:23,873
HI, RIN.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING UP
SO EARLY?

265
00:16:23,906 --> 00:16:25,840
I JUST COULDN'T
GET TO SLEEP, IS ALL.

266
00:16:25,873 --> 00:16:28,173
<i>- ARE YOU WORRIED</i>
<i>ABOUT SOMETHING?</i>
- JUST REMEMBERING...

267
00:16:28,206 --> 00:16:29,906
STUFF ABOUT MY OLD MAN.

268
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:32,440
OLD MAN?
YOU MEAN SHIRO?

269
00:16:32,473 --> 00:16:33,740
YEAH.

270
00:16:33,773 --> 00:16:36,806
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

271
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,706
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

272
00:16:43,206 --> 00:16:45,473
IT'S OKAY, RIN.
JUST CALM DOWN NOW.

273
00:16:45,506 --> 00:16:48,640
SHUT UP!
GET AWAY!
DON'T COME NEAR ME!

274
00:16:48,673 --> 00:16:50,640
[ SHOUTING ]

275
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,640
EASY.

276
00:16:54,673 --> 00:16:56,373
RIN!

277
00:16:56,406 --> 00:16:57,740
DAD.

278
00:16:57,773 --> 00:17:00,240
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

279
00:17:00,273 --> 00:17:03,706
YOU HIT YOUR FRIEND SO HARD
HE'S IN THE HOSPITAL NOW,
SUFFERING.

280
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:07,140
THAT KID
ISN'T MY FRIEND!
WHAT?

281
00:17:07,173 --> 00:17:11,173
THIS IS ALL HIS FAULT.
HE CALLED ME A DEMON, A MONSTER.

282
00:17:11,206 --> 00:17:13,273
HE DESERVED IT,
AND I'D DO IT AGAIN!

283
00:17:13,306 --> 00:17:15,373
IT'S YOUR FAULT
FOR RAISING A HAND TO HIM.

284
00:17:16,706 --> 00:17:18,406
[ SCREAMING ]

285
00:17:20,573 --> 00:17:21,706
[ WOMAN ]
LOOK OUT!

286
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,973
[ WOMAN #2 ]
HOW DO YOU EVEN RAISE
A CHILD LIKE THAT?

287
00:17:24,006 --> 00:17:26,206
LOOK AT HIM.
HE REALLY LOOKS LIKE A DEVIL.

288
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:29,140
IT'S DANGEROUS, LADIES.
PLEASE STAY BACK.

289
00:17:35,373 --> 00:17:37,240
[ SCREAMING ]

290
00:17:37,273 --> 00:17:38,106
OW!

291
00:17:39,173 --> 00:17:41,373
[ GASPS ]
[ GRUNTING ]

292
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:46,140
- DAD?
- PSYCH! I'M JUST KIDDING!

293
00:17:46,173 --> 00:17:48,273
I TRICKED YOU.
[ LAUGHS ]

294
00:17:48,306 --> 00:17:51,773
- WERE YOU SCARED?
- HUH?

295
00:17:51,806 --> 00:17:55,306
LISTEN, RIN, IF YOU
DON'T CHANGE YOUR WAYS,

296
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:58,140
YOU'RE GONNA FIND YOURSELF
ALL ALONE SOMEDAY.

297
00:17:58,173 --> 00:18:01,306
INSTEAD OF USING YOUR POWER
TO HURT OTHERS,

298
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:04,373
YOU SHOULD BE USING IT
TO HELP THEM.

299
00:18:04,406 --> 00:18:06,740
I WANT YOU TO HAVE
A WHOLE BUNCH OF FRIENDS.

300
00:18:06,773 --> 00:18:11,906
I WANT YOU TO GROW UP
TO BE A COOL GUY, THE ONE
THE GIRLS GO CRAZY FOR.

301
00:18:11,940 --> 00:18:14,106
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

302
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:17,073
HOW AM I EVER GONNA BE
SOMEONE LIKE THAT?

303
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:27,406
YOU TRY.
IF YOU WORK HARD
AND ARE NICE TO PEOPLE,

304
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:31,540
THEN BEFORE YOU EVEN KNOW IT,
YOU'LL BE THAT COOL GUY
WITH ALL THE FRIENDS.

305
00:18:36,973 --> 00:18:38,506
I CAN'T HOLD IT.

306
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:40,940
I'M GONNA NEED
THAT AMBULANCE AFTER ALL.

307
00:18:40,973 --> 00:18:42,406
DAD! HANG ON!

308
00:18:45,873 --> 00:18:47,906
YOU HAVE SOME BROKEN RIBS,
SO LIE STILL.

309
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:49,806
- SERIOUSLY?
- DAD!

310
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:53,973
OH, NOW, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO LOOK SO SCARED, KIDDO.
I'M ALL RIGHT,

311
00:18:54,006 --> 00:18:57,340
YOU NEED A HECK OF A LOT MORE
THAN THOSE LITTLE FISTS
TO TAKE ME DOWN.

312
00:18:57,373 --> 00:18:59,540
BUT THEY SAID YOUR RIBS
ARE BROKEN!

313
00:18:59,573 --> 00:19:01,973
I BROKE 'EM ON PURPOSE
'CAUSE I WAS PUMPED UP.

314
00:19:02,006 --> 00:19:05,573
NOW I GET TO GO TO THE HOSPITAL
AND HAVE A NURSE
WITH HUGE BOOBS LOOK AFTER ME.

315
00:19:05,606 --> 00:19:06,640
OW!

316
00:19:06,673 --> 00:19:08,606
GENTLY, BOYS.
GENTLY.

317
00:19:11,340 --> 00:19:13,373
[ SIREN WAILS ]

318
00:19:17,473 --> 00:19:20,606
I WANTED TO GROW UP
TO BE COOL...

319
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:22,606
JUST LIKE MY OLD MAN.

320
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:24,506
[ AMAIMON ]
I DON'T UNDERSTAND IT.

321
00:19:24,540 --> 00:19:28,540
WHY WOULD FATHER
AND MY BIG BROTHER
BE SO OBSESSED WITH THIS ONE?

322
00:19:28,573 --> 00:19:31,340
AND WE'LL USE HIM AS A WEAPON
FOR THE ORDER.

323
00:19:31,373 --> 00:19:33,840
[ SHURA ]
HERE'S YOUR CHANCE
TO PROVE IT, KID--

324
00:19:33,873 --> 00:19:35,640
THAT SHIRO WAS RIGHT
ABOUT YOU ALL ALONG.

325
00:19:37,173 --> 00:19:40,006
[ YAWNS ]
[ CHUCKLES ]

326
00:19:45,206 --> 00:19:48,240
I CAN THINK ABOUT IT ALL NIGHT,
BUT I WON'T HAVE AN ANSWER.

327
00:19:48,273 --> 00:19:51,273
MY BRAIN'S NOT BIG ENOUGH.

328
00:19:51,306 --> 00:19:53,973
COME ON.
LET'S GO HAVE SOME FUN.

329
00:19:54,006 --> 00:19:56,640
OKAY! LET'S PLAY!
LET'S PLAY!

330
00:19:58,106 --> 00:20:00,640
- <i>I'M READY, RIN!</i>
- LET'S GO!

331
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:06,106
ALL I CAN DO FOR NOW
IS SHAKE IT OFF,
KEEP A CLEAR HEAD...

332
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:08,373
AND KEEP MOVING FORWARD.

333
00:20:10,206 --> 00:20:12,406
[ SHURA ]
HOW'S EVERYONE DOING?
I'VE BEEN TRANSFERRED...

334
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:15,440
FROM VATICAN HEADQUARTERS
TO THE JAPAN BRANCH.

335
00:20:15,473 --> 00:20:19,506
MY NAME IS SHURA KIRIGAKURE,
AND I'M 18 YEARS OLD.

336
00:20:19,540 --> 00:20:23,640
NAH, I'M KIDDING.
I'VE BEEN IN CLASS WITH Y'ALL
FOR THE LAST THREE MONTHS,

337
00:20:23,673 --> 00:20:25,340
SO, TECHNICALLY,
WE ALREADY MET.

338
00:20:25,373 --> 00:20:27,273
NICE TO MEET YOU AGAIN!
[ LAUGHS ]

339
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:33,073
ANYWHO, I'LL BE TEACHING
YOU GUYS MAGIC CIRCLES
AND SEALS, AND--

340
00:20:33,106 --> 00:20:35,306
[ GROANS ]
YEAH, SWORDSMANSHIP TOO.

341
00:20:35,340 --> 00:20:37,040
OH, KILL ME NOW.

342
00:20:37,073 --> 00:20:40,973
- MS. KIRIGAKURE?
- HMM? YEAH, WHAT'S UP,
MR. SUGURO?

343
00:20:41,006 --> 00:20:44,240
SO WHY WERE YOU PRETENDING
TO BE A STUDENT?

344
00:20:44,273 --> 00:20:46,673
GROWN-UPS HAVE
THEIR REASONS, YOU KNOW?

345
00:20:46,706 --> 00:20:48,406
YOU WOULDN'T
UNDERSTAND, KID.

346
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,606
[ STUTTERS ]
MA'AM?

347
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:52,640
PROFESSOR NOIHAUS
WAS TEACHING
MAGIC CIRCLES AND SEALS.

348
00:20:52,673 --> 00:20:55,906
CHANGING INSTRUCTORS
MID-SEMESTER
IS KIND OF CONFUSING.

349
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:58,140
THE PROFESSOR'S
ON MATERNITY LEAVE.

350
00:20:58,173 --> 00:21:01,340
YEAH!
BUT PROFESSOR NOIHAUS
IS A MAN!

351
00:21:01,373 --> 00:21:04,006
OH. OKAY, THEN.
UH, PATERNITY LEAVE.

352
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:07,440
OR WHATEVER.
WHAT DO I KNOW?
ASK THE PRECEPT!

353
00:21:07,473 --> 00:21:09,473
RIN'S REALLY LATE.

354
00:21:09,506 --> 00:21:10,640
[ DOOR OPENS ]

355
00:21:10,673 --> 00:21:12,006
[ RIN ]
SORRY I'M LATE,

356
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,473
[ SHIEMI ]
RIN!

357
00:21:13,506 --> 00:21:16,073
YOU SEE, I DIDN'T GET
MUCH SLEEP LAST NIGHT,

358
00:21:16,106 --> 00:21:18,573
AND I WENT UP TO THE ROOF
TO TAKE A NAP,

359
00:21:18,606 --> 00:21:22,340
BUT NO ONE CAME TO WAKE ME UP,
EVEN AFTER HOMEROOM ENDED.

360
00:21:22,373 --> 00:21:24,840
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO STAND OUT THERE.
COME ON IN.

361
00:21:24,873 --> 00:21:26,873
I WON'T GET MAD AT YOU.
[ GASPS ]

362
00:21:26,906 --> 00:21:29,040
IT'S YOU!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

363
00:21:29,073 --> 00:21:30,773
NEVER MIND.
SIT YOUR ASS DOWN ALREADY.

364
00:21:30,806 --> 00:21:32,440
OH.

365
00:21:33,773 --> 00:21:35,806
RIN,

366
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:37,806
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE ALL HEALED UP?

367
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:39,640
HUH?
OH, YEAH, IT'S ALL GOOD.

368
00:21:39,673 --> 00:21:41,640
WHY?
[ GIGGLES ]

369
00:21:41,673 --> 00:21:43,306
AS LONG AS YOU'RE OKAY.

370
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:46,606
IS IT ME, OR DOES HE SEEM
A LITTLE DIFFERENT TODAY?

371
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:49,340
MAYBE HE SUFFERED
SOME KIND OF SHOCK OR SOMETHING.

372
00:21:49,373 --> 00:21:50,706
DO YOU THINK SO?

373
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:52,173
NOW THAT WE'RE ALL HERE,

374
00:21:52,206 --> 00:21:54,940
HOW ABOUT WE GET
THIS PARTY STARTED
AND DO SOME LEARNING?

375
00:21:54,973 --> 00:21:59,473
LET'S HAVE MR. TARDY READ
THE CHAPTER ON GEOMANCY
FROM SEAL ARTS 101.

376
00:21:59,506 --> 00:22:01,340
HIT IT, OKUMURA.

377
00:22:01,373 --> 00:22:02,673
OKAY.

378
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:09,340
IF IT'LL HELP ME BECOME
A PALADIN, I'LL DO IT.

379
00:22:09,373 --> 00:22:11,406
HERE GOES!

380
00:22:16,806 --> 00:22:17,706
[ WOMAN ]

381
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:22,440
♪ [ CHORUS SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

382
00:23:41,406 --> 00:23:45,540
"ACCORDING
TO ANCIENT LITERATURE
ON GEE-O-MAN"--

383
00:23:45,573 --> 00:23:47,506
OH, HOLD ON.
"GEE-O-MAN"--

384
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:50,440
- GEOMANCY.
- SEE THAT?
HE'S THE SAME AS HE EVER WAS.

385
00:23:50,473 --> 00:23:53,040
YOU'RE RIGHT.
I GUESS IT WAS ME AFTER ALL.

386
00:23:53,073 --> 00:23:55,106
[ BLUBBERING ]

387
00:23:57,173 --> 00:23:59,640
UH-UH.
THAT WASN'T MY FAULT.

388
00:24:02,106 --> 00:24:04,340
[ YUKIO ]
I'M SURE YOU'RE ALL EXCITED
ABOUT SUMMER VACATION.

389
00:24:04,373 --> 00:24:07,573
[ RIN ]
THIS IS GONNA BE RAD!
LIKE GOING ON A PICNIC!

390
00:24:07,606 --> 00:24:09,606
[ SHURA ]
I DON'T THINK YOU UNDERSTAND
THE SITUATION.

391
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:12,473
SO YOU'D BETTER NOT
BE FLAMING UP OUT THERE, KID.

392
00:24:12,506 --> 00:24:15,440
[ SUGURO ]
OKUMURA, WHAT THE HELL
WAS THAT?

